{"tid":557432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大埔巴士車禍】路祭現場多出一塊靈牌　事主仍在手術中","createTime":"2018-02-11T10:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T11:52:11.000Z","uid":51271,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"33054c4c63dd0bc8e7684ba5b898971d62f10b7f","tid":557432,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:48:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180211/s00001/1518343684469\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180211%2Fs00001%2F1518343684469&d=kiKBxHDjUeexk8ASMQHTrzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=68bd3770\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180211%2Fs00001%2F1518343684469&h=a44047b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180211/s00001/1518343684469</a><br />\n<br />\n大埔公路昨日傍晚發生嚴重車禍，至今有19人死亡、60多人受傷。今日下午約4時，有逾百人在車禍現場路祭，現場卻置有20個靈牌。本報致電政府新聞處查詢，對方引述根據醫管局提供最新資料回覆，目前車禍死者數目仍為19人。消息人士透露，第20個牌位屬於一名姓馮男子，事主現時仍在醫院接受手術。"},{"pid":"486291c7f3d65157f4eb1e793438bccf531f9ad7","tid":557432,"uid":60545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:50:02.000Z","msg":"即係話佢死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8e42264cd41e2e76c3187641aa7d7683170fa2","tid":557432,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:51:11.000Z","msg":"今朝清晨仲話唔係19<br />\n依家就<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504d7fb72f8691f23ff192b67f2985a66052467e","tid":557432,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:51:45.000Z","msg":"呢啲儀式就算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"2dc151e0cf9ff86b075c3efd3df0b7ba83439cdf","tid":557432,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:52:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58f58dea0f80d034a0d241ee03